	| colorFormat_YUV420 	= 01 |
	| colorFormat_YUV444 	= 10 |
	| colorFormat_YUV422 	= 11 |

	|  bpc_6bpc	 = 00  |
	|  bpc_8bpc  = 01  |
	|  bpc_10bpc = 10  |
	|  bpc_12bpc = 11  |

	pixelRepMode (0 = Not a Pixel Replicated Mode, 1 = Pixel Replicated Mode) -->
